[%@library error_code[![:en]constructor[:zh_CN]构造函数]]
[codeblock:declaration]
error_code() noexcept;
[codeblock:end]

[enter:description]
[para:effects]
[:en] Constructs an object of type [`error_code].
[:zh_CN] 构造 [`error_code] 类型的一个对象。

[para:postconditions]
[:en] [`val_ == 0] and [`cat_ == &system_category()].
[:zh_CN] [`val_ == 0] 并且 [`cat_ == &system_category()]。
[exit:description]

[%@library error_code[![:en]constructor[:zh_CN]构造函数]]
[codeblock:declaration]
error_code(int val, const error_category& cat) noexcept;
[codeblock:end]

[enter:description]
[para:effects]
[:en] Constructs an object of type [`error_code].
[:zh_CN] 构造 [`error_code] 类型的一个对象。

[para:postconditions]
[:en] [`val_ == val] and [`cat_ == &cat].
[:zh_CN] [`val_ == val] 并且 [`cat_ == &cat]。
[exit:description]

[%@library error_code[![:en]constructor[:zh_CN]构造函数]]
[codeblock:declaration]
template<class ErrorCodeEnum>
  error_code(ErrorCodeEnum e) noexcept;
[codeblock:end]

[enter:description]
[para:effects]
[:en] Constructs an object of type [`error_code].
[:zh_CN] 构造 [`error_code] 类型的一个对象。

[para:postconditions]
[:en] [`*this == make_error_code(e)].
[:zh_CN] [`*this == make_error_code(e)]。

[para:remarks]
[:en] This constructor shall not participate in overload resolution unless
[`is_error_code_enum_v<ErrorCodeEnum>] is [`true].
[:zh_CN] 除非 [`is_error_code_enum_v<ErrorCodeEnum>] 为 [`true]，否则这个
构造函数不能参与重载决议。
[exit:description]
